### AgentBin A2A Test File
### Use with VS Code REST Client extension (humao.rest-client)
### Toggle @baseUrl between local and Azure as needed.

@baseUrl = https://agentbin.greensmoke-1163cb63.eastus.azurecontainerapps.io
# @baseUrl = http://localhost:5000

### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
### HEALTH CHECK
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
### AGENT CARDS — JSON-RPC (v1.0)
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### Echo Agent Card (JSON-RPC well-known)
GET {{baseUrl}}/echo/.well-known/agent-card.json
A2A-Version: 1.0

### Spec Agent Card (JSON-RPC well-known)
GET {{baseUrl}}/spec/.well-known/agent-card.json
A2A-Version: 1.0

### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
### AGENT CARDS — REST binding
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### Echo Agent Card (REST)
GET {{baseUrl}}/echo/v1/card
A2A-Version: 1.0

### Spec Agent Card (REST)
GET {{baseUrl}}/spec/v1/card
A2A-Version: 1.0

### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
### AGENT CARDS — v0.3 (no A2A-Version header)
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### Echo Agent Card (v0.3 — has protocolVersion, url at top level)
GET {{baseUrl}}/echo/.well-known/agent-card.json

### Spec Agent Card (v0.3)
GET {{baseUrl}}/spec/.well-known/agent-card.json

### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
### JSON-RPC — ECHO AGENT
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### Echo — simple message (JSON-RPC)
POST {{baseUrl}}/echo
Content-Type: application/json
A2A-Version: 1.0

{
  "jsonrpc": "2.0",
  "method": "SendMessage",
  "id": "echo-v10-1",
  "params": {
    "message": {
      "messageId": "msg-echo-v10-1",
      "role": "ROLE_USER",
      "parts": [{ "text": "Hello from v1.0 client!" }]
    }
  }
}

### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
### REST — ECHO AGENT
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### Echo — simple message (REST)
POST {{baseUrl}}/echo/v1/message:send
Content-Type: application/json
A2A-Version: 1.0

{
  "message": {
    "messageId": "msg-echo-rest-1",
    "role": "ROLE_USER",
    "parts": [{ "text": "Hello from REST client!" }]
  }
}

