### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
### JSON-RPC — SPEC AGENT: task-lifecycle
### Full task state machine: submitted → working → completed
### Returns a task with artifacts
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### Task Lifecycle (JSON-RPC)
# @name taskLifecycleV10
POST {{baseUrl}}/spec
Content-Type: application/json
A2A-Version: 1.0

{
  "jsonrpc": "2.0",
  "method": "SendMessage",
  "id": "task-lc-v10",
  "params": {
    "message": {
      "messageId": "msg-lc-1",
      "role": "ROLE_USER",
      "parts": [{ "text": "task-lifecycle process this data" }]
    }
  }
}

### Task Lifecycle (REST)
POST {{baseUrl}}/spec/v1/message:send
Content-Type: application/json
A2A-Version: 1.0

{
  "message": {
    "messageId": "msg-lc-rest-1",
    "role": "ROLE_USER",
    "parts": [{ "text": "task-lifecycle process this data" }]
  }
}

### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
### GetTask — retrieve previously created task
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

@taskLifecycleTaskId = {{taskLifecycleV10.response.body.$.result.task.id}}

### GetTask (JSON-RPC)
POST {{baseUrl}}/spec
Content-Type: application/json
A2A-Version: 1.0

{
  "jsonrpc": "2.0",
  "method": "GetTask",
  "id": "get-task-1",
  "params": {
    "id": "{{taskLifecycleTaskId}}"
  }
}

### GetTask (REST)
GET {{baseUrl}}/spec/v1/tasks/{{taskLifecycleTaskId}}
A2A-Version: 1.0

