### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
### SPEC AGENT: task-cancel
### ⚠ BLOCKED: .NET SDK doesn't support returnImmediately.
### The server completes tasks synchronously, so there's never a
### task in WORKING state for the client to cancel.
### task-cancel skill hangs until timeout waiting for cancellation.
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### Task Cancel — Start task (JSON-RPC)
### ⚠ This request will HANG — server waits for cancel that can't come
# POST {{baseUrl}}/spec
# Content-Type: application/json
# A2A-Version: 1.0
#
# {
#   "jsonrpc": "2.0",
#   "method": "SendMessage",
#   "id": "task-cancel-start",
#   "params": {
#     "message": {
#       "messageId": "msg-cancel-1",
#       "role": "ROLE_USER",
#       "parts": [{ "text": "task-cancel start" }]
#     },
#     "configuration": { "returnImmediately": true }
#   }
# }

### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
### SPEC AGENT: multi-turn
### Step 1: Start → returns INPUT_REQUIRED
### Step 2: Follow-up with taskId INSIDE message → more input
### Step 3: Say "done" with taskId → COMPLETED
### NOTE: taskId goes inside message object, not at params level
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### Multi-Turn — Step 1: Start (JSON-RPC)
# @name multiTurnStartV10
POST {{baseUrl}}/spec
Content-Type: application/json
A2A-Version: 1.0

{
  "jsonrpc": "2.0",
  "method": "SendMessage",
  "id": "mt-start",
  "params": {
    "message": {
      "messageId": "msg-mt-1",
      "role": "ROLE_USER",
      "parts": [{ "text": "multi-turn start conversation" }]
    }
  }
}

@multiTurnTaskIdV10 = {{multiTurnStartV10.response.body.$.result.task.id}}

### Multi-Turn — Step 2: Follow-up (taskId inside message)
POST {{baseUrl}}/spec
Content-Type: application/json
A2A-Version: 1.0

{
  "jsonrpc": "2.0",
  "method": "SendMessage",
  "id": "mt-reply",
  "params": {
    "message": {
      "messageId": "msg-mt-2",
      "role": "ROLE_USER",
      "parts": [{ "text": "here is more input" }],
      "taskId": "{{multiTurnTaskIdV10}}"
    }
  }
}

### Multi-Turn — Step 3: Complete (say "done")
POST {{baseUrl}}/spec
Content-Type: application/json
A2A-Version: 1.0

{
  "jsonrpc": "2.0",
  "method": "SendMessage",
  "id": "mt-done",
  "params": {
    "message": {
      "messageId": "msg-mt-3",
      "role": "ROLE_USER",
      "parts": [{ "text": "done" }],
      "taskId": "{{multiTurnTaskIdV10}}"
    }
  }
}

### Multi-Turn — Step 1: Start (REST)
# @name multiTurnStartRest
POST {{baseUrl}}/spec/v1/message:send
Content-Type: application/json
A2A-Version: 1.0

{
  "message": {
    "messageId": "msg-mt-rest-1",
    "role": "ROLE_USER",
    "parts": [{ "text": "multi-turn start conversation" }]
  }
}

@multiTurnRestTaskId = {{multiTurnStartRest.response.body.$.task.id}}

### Multi-Turn — Step 2: Follow-up (REST)
POST {{baseUrl}}/spec/v1/message:send
Content-Type: application/json
A2A-Version: 1.0

{
  "message": {
    "messageId": "msg-mt-rest-2",
    "role": "ROLE_USER",
    "parts": [{ "text": "here is REST input" }],
    "taskId": "{{multiTurnRestTaskId}}"
  }
}

### Multi-Turn — Step 3: Complete (REST)
POST {{baseUrl}}/spec/v1/message:send
Content-Type: application/json
A2A-Version: 1.0

{
  "message": {
    "messageId": "msg-mt-rest-3",
    "role": "ROLE_USER",
    "parts": [{ "text": "done" }],
    "taskId": "{{multiTurnRestTaskId}}"
  }
}

### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
### SPEC AGENT: streaming
### SSE response with status updates and artifact chunks
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### Streaming (JSON-RPC)
POST {{baseUrl}}/spec
Content-Type: application/json
A2A-Version: 1.0

{
  "jsonrpc": "2.0",
  "method": "SendStreamingMessage",
  "id": "stream-v10",
  "params": {
    "message": {
      "messageId": "msg-stream-1",
      "role": "ROLE_USER",
      "parts": [{ "text": "streaming generate output" }]
    }
  }
}

### Streaming (REST)
POST {{baseUrl}}/spec/v1/message:stream
Content-Type: application/json
A2A-Version: 1.0
Accept: text/event-stream

{
  "message": {
    "messageId": "msg-stream-rest-1",
    "role": "ROLE_USER",
    "parts": [{ "text": "streaming generate output" }]
  }
}

### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
### SPEC AGENT: long-running
### ⚠ LIMITATION: Returns completed task synchronously because
### .NET SDK doesn't support returnImmediately. Ideally this
### would return WORKING and the client would poll with GetTask.
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### Long Running (JSON-RPC) — completes synchronously (~5s)
POST {{baseUrl}}/spec
Content-Type: application/json
A2A-Version: 1.0

{
  "jsonrpc": "2.0",
  "method": "SendMessage",
  "id": "long-start",
  "params": {
    "message": {
      "messageId": "msg-long-1",
      "role": "ROLE_USER",
      "parts": [{ "text": "long-running start process" }]
    }
  }
}

