### ListTasks
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### ListTasks — all tasks (JSON-RPC)
POST {{baseUrl}}/spec
Content-Type: application/json
A2A-Version: 1.0

{
  "jsonrpc": "2.0",
  "method": "ListTasks",
  "id": "list-all",
  "params": {}
}

