### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
### ERROR HANDLING
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### GetTask — not found (JSON-RPC)
POST {{baseUrl}}/spec
Content-Type: application/json
A2A-Version: 1.0

{
  "jsonrpc": "2.0",
  "method": "GetTask",
  "id": "get-missing",
  "params": {
    "id": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000"
  }
}

### GetTask — not found (REST → 404)
GET {{baseUrl}}/spec/v1/tasks/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
A2A-Version: 1.0

### CancelTask — not found (JSON-RPC)
POST {{baseUrl}}/spec
Content-Type: application/json
A2A-Version: 1.0

{
  "jsonrpc": "2.0",
  "method": "CancelTask",
  "id": "cancel-missing",
  "params": {
    "id": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000"
  }
}

### CancelTask — completed task (JSON-RPC, should error)
POST {{baseUrl}}/spec
Content-Type: application/json
A2A-Version: 1.0

{
  "jsonrpc": "2.0",
  "method": "CancelTask",
  "id": "cancel-completed",
  "params": {
    "id": "{{taskLifecycleTaskId}}"
  }
}

### CancelTask — not found (REST → 404)
POST {{baseUrl}}/spec/v1/tasks/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000:cancel
Content-Type: application/json
A2A-Version: 1.0

### Unknown method (JSON-RPC → -32601)
POST {{baseUrl}}/spec
Content-Type: application/json
A2A-Version: 1.0

{
  "jsonrpc": "2.0",
  "method": "DoSomethingFake",
  "id": "fake-1",
  "params": {}
}

### Invalid JSON (JSON-RPC → should be -32700 but returns -32603)
POST {{baseUrl}}/spec
Content-Type: application/json
A2A-Version: 1.0

not valid json at all

### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
### v0.3 — ECHO AGENT
### No A2A-Version header, kebab-case method, lowercase role,
### parts with "kind" discriminator
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### Echo (v0.3)
POST {{baseUrl}}/echo
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "jsonrpc": "2.0",
  "method": "message/send",
  "id": "echo-v03-1",
  "params": {
    "message": {
      "messageId": "msg-echo-v03-1",
      "role": "user",
      "parts": [{ "kind": "text", "text": "Hello from v0.3 client!" }]
    }
  }
}

